title: Pandol
desciption: Panadol Extra is a mild analgesic and antipyretic formulated to give extra pain relief. The soluble tablets are recommended for the treatment of most painful and febrile conditions, for example, headache including migraine, backache, toothache, colds and influenza, sore throat, rheumatic pain and dysmenorrhoea.

title: Crocin Pain relief
desciption: Crocin Advance Tablet is a medicine used to relieve pain and to reduce fever. It is used to treat many conditions such as headache, body ache, toothache and common cold. It works by inhibiting the release of certain chemical that cause pain and fever.

title: Aclomax
desciption: Aclomax is indicated for the treatment of the pain of osteoarthritis of the knee(s).

title: Voltaren
desciption: If you are in pain, Voltaren Pain Gel will keep your back free so that you can concentrate on the essentials. Voltaren pain gel has a 3-fold effect: it stops the pain, fights its most common cause, the inflammation and promotes healing.

title: Bayer Aspirin
desciption: Aspirin, also known as acetylsalicylic acid (ASA), is a medication used to reduce pain, fever, or inflammation. Specific inflammatory conditions which aspirin is used to treat include Kawasaki disease, pericarditis, and rheumatic fever.
